        "details": "<p>Our AI-powered mockup generator takes the guesswork out of product visualization. Using advanced rendering technology, it seamlessly applies your designs to both hard goods and apparel, ensuring a <strong>r</strong>ealistic, high-resolution preview every time.</p><p>With smart color customization, you can instantly adjust the color of your product to match different variations, making it easy to showcase multiple options without needing separate images. The AI automatically adjusts lighting, shadows, and textures to ensure your design looks natural and true to life—just like a professionally staged product photo.</p><p>Whether you're preparing for a launch, updating your online store, or creating marketing materials, our AI ensures crisp, detailed mockups in seconds, helping you sell with confidence.</p>",
        "paddingTop": 60,
        "paddingBottom": 48
      }
    },
